{"tid":1394213,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"8月3號Seasons for Change 《Petals of Tomorrow 》CD release show","createTime":"2019-08-01T10:43:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T13:47:57.000Z","uid":202348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b404bf424f6346ca3a8036f93c8e22ae0ec7bf","tid":1394213,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:43:43.000Z","msg":"🔥🔥門票火熱預售中🔥🔥 <br />\n睽違三年, 繼2016年發佈首張EP《Timeless Collective》, 本地另類搖滾樂團Seasons for Change迎來全新專輯《Petals of Tomorrow》, 並鐵定於8月3日於九展Music Zone舉辦CD Release Show, 讓一眾樂迷現場感受Seasons for Change更趨成熟卻不失實驗風格的獨特音樂! <br />\n日期 Date: August 3, 2019<br />\n時間 Time: 8:00pm (Door open at 7:30pm)<br />\n地點 Venue: Music Zone @ KITEC 九龍灣國際展貿中心<br />\n門票 Ticket: HK$280 <br />\n特別嘉賓 Guest: OBSESS (TW), The Priceless Boat<br />\n網上售票 Online Ticketing：<a href=\"https://tickcats.co/ticket/seasonsforchange/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftickcats.co%2Fticket%2Fseasonsforchange%2F&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=4fa038e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tickcats.co/ticket/seasonsforchange/</a><br />\n實體門票 Physical Ticketing：Infree Records, 觸STUDIO<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Seasons for Change 真係好高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n有無人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c34c06c1e7f10c49ff316d787ee5d5b54d90037d","tid":1394213,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T10:44:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課</span>[/size=5]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">感謝靚聲絲打讀出 hashtag 無限loop</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-612048585/loop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-612048585%2Floop&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEZR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=47affefb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https